<item>
            <title>[HADOOP-9249] hadoop-maven-plugins version-info goal causes build failure when running with Clover</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HADOOP-9249</link>
                <project id="12310240" key="HADOOP">Hadoop Common</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Running Maven with the -Pclover option for code coverage causes the build to fail because of not finding a Clover class while running hadoop-maven-plugins version-info.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12629311">HADOOP-9249</key>
            <summary>hadoop-maven-plugins version-info goal causes build failure when running with Clover</summary>
